'''卢卡斯艺术公司'''（LucasArts Entertainment Company, LLC）<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.lucasarts.com/company/release/news20000620.html|title=LucasArts Entertainment Company Names New Director Of Business Affairs|date=June 20, 2000|publisher=LucasArts|accessdate=2009-08-30|archive-date=2009-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928072220/http://www.lucasarts.com/company/release/news20000620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一間[[美國|美國]]的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]][[電子遊戲發行商|發行]]<ref name="Tiny Death Star release">{{cite web |url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/Tiny-Death-Star-Available-For-Android |title=Tiny Death Star Available For Android |date=2013-10-11 |accessdate=2013-10-12 |publisher=The International House of Mojo |archive-date=2013-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013112123/http://mixnmojo.com/news/Tiny-Death-Star-Available-For-Android |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[品牌授權|授權]]公司<ref>{{cite web |url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/games/lucusarts-vet-turns-to-kickstarter-to-revive-a-vampyre-story/ |date=2013-06-21 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |title=LucasArts vet turns to Kickstarter to revive a ‘Vampyre Story’ |publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] |archive-date=2013-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623005511/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/games/lucusarts-vet-turns-to-kickstarter-to-revive-a-vampyre-story/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，總部位於[[加利福尼亞州|加州]][[舊金山|舊金山]]。直到2013年為止，LucasArts亦同時為一間[[游戏开发者|電子遊戲開發公司]]。LucasArts曾以[[圖形冒險遊戲|圖形冒險遊戲]]作品聞名，並曾推出多款根據《[[星際大戰|星際大戰]]》和《[[印第安納瓊斯|印第安納瓊斯]]》系列改編的遊戲作品。

LucasArts在1982年由[[喬治·盧卡斯|喬治·盧卡斯]]創立，當時名為「盧卡斯影業遊戲」，是隸屬于[[盧卡斯影業|盧卡斯影業]]旗下的電子遊戲開發團隊。公司的主席由最初盧卡斯本人擔任。在1990年盧卡斯各相關公司改組時，盧卡斯影業遊戲部門重新命名為LucasArts。

2012年，LucasArts隨著母公司盧卡斯影業被[[華特迪士尼公司|華特迪士尼公司]]收購。2013年4月3日，迪士尼終止了所有LucasArts的內部開發計劃，並資遣了多數的員工。然而，LucasArts仍然以授權公司的身份繼續營運。<ref name="CNET">{{cite web|last=Terdiman|first=Daniel|title=Disney shuttering LucasArts, moving to licensed games model|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57577786-235/disney-shuttering-lucasarts-moving-to-licensed-games-model/|publisher=CNET|accessdate=2013-04-03|archive-date=2013-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130404094649/http://news.cnet.com/8301-10797_3-57577786-235/disney-shuttering-lucasarts-moving-to-licensed-games-model/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Wrap>{{cite news|last=Shaw|first=Lucas|title=LucasArts to Cease Making Games, Will Lay Off Most of Staff|url=http://www.thewrap.com/media/article/lucasarts-cease-making-games-will-lay-most-staff-83891|accessdate=2013-04-03|newspaper=The Wrap|date=2013-04-03|archive-date=2013-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406040021/http://www.thewrap.com/media/article/lucasarts-cease-making-games-will-lay-most-staff-83891|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=IBT>{{cite news|last=Neal|first=Ryan W.|title=Disney Closes LucasArts, Video Game Arm of LucasFilm, Cancels Star Wars Games|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/disney-closes-lucasarts-video-game-arm-lucasfilm-cancels-star-wars-games-1169515|accessdate=2013-04-03|newspaper=International Business Times|date=2013-04-03|archive-date=2013-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406030728/http://www.ibtimes.com/disney-closes-lucasarts-video-game-arm-lucasfilm-cancels-star-wars-games-1169515|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在LucasArts轉型為授權公司後，核心市場方面的《星際大戰》系列遊戲由[[藝電|藝電]]（Electronic Arts）取得獨家授權並負責開發製作。休閒遊戲市場方面的系列作品則由[[迪士尼互動工作室|迪士尼互動工作室]]取得開發權，LucasArts保留了授權的權利。<ref name="Verge EA">{{cite web|title=EA takes helm from LucasArts, will exclusively develop future 'Star Wars' games|url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/6/4306040/electronic-arts-gets-exclusive-deal-to-develop-star-wars-video-games|accessdate=2013-05-06|publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|date=2013-05-06|archive-date=2013-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507184058/http://www.theverge.com/2013/5/6/4306040/electronic-arts-gets-exclusive-deal-to-develop-star-wars-video-games|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Mojo EA">{{cite web|title=We're probably all about EA|url=http://mixnmojo.com/news/Were-probably-all-about-EA|accessdate=2013-05-06|publisher=The International House of Mojo|date=2013-05-06|archive-date=2013-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617053004/http://mixnmojo.com/news/Were-probably-all-about-EA|dead-url=yes}}</ref>根據其他盧卡斯影業作品改編的電子遊戲開發則由迪士尼互動工作室接手或授權給第三方廠商。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/04/03/disney-lucasarts-closing-star-wars/2050055/ |title=Game Over For LucasArts Studio |publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=2013-04-03 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607174105/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/04/03/disney-lucasarts-closing-star-wars/2050055/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

